üì¶ API Reference
----------------
The server-side API provides the following endpoints:
* **POST /transcribe**: Transcribes audio data and returns the text transcription.
* **GET /health**: Returns the health status of the server.

### API Documentation
The API documentation is available at [https://via.placeholder.com/api/docs](https://via.placeholder.com/api/docs).

